confident.

04:27.438 --> 04:31.932
- Did the chap from Newsday ever call?
- I'll check my machine.

04:33.177 --> 04:36.013
Is this a real interview
or some cute guy...

04:36.013 --> 04:38.015
- you're setting me up with?
- Please, Julianne.

04:38.015 --> 04:40.851
I don't send you men anymore.
