22:09.932 --> 22:12.335
being comfortable...

22:12.335 --> 22:14.326
with the yucky love stuff.

22:17.673 --> 22:19.275
all right.

22:19.275 --> 22:21.766
And I am.

22:24.547 --> 22:28.251
