23:58.841 --> 24:04.380
Don't architects find a degree
sort of an asset?

24:04.380 --> 24:08.684
I travel every week. Got college ball,
motor sports, training camps.

24:08.684 --> 24:11.687
I think the most important thing
is for us to be together.

24:11.687 --> 24:16.559
Say, Pinky, I wanna hear you sing.
Come on.

24:16.559 --> 24:18.823
Kimmy hates to sing.
She hates it.

24:22.832 --> 24:24.901
all right, folks.
Everybody...

24:24.901 --> 24:29.472
my bride-to-be here
is about to kick some ass on--

24:29.472 --> 24:31.741
What?
It will be fun.

24:31.741 --> 24:34.410
No, she doesn't want to, Michael.
Leave her alone.

24:34.410 --> 24:37.380
Come on.
Ladies and gentlemen...

24:37.380 --> 24:41.417
Please give it up for the dazzling
vocal stylings...

24:41.417 --> 24:43.749
of Miss Kimberly Wallace!

24:48.691 --> 24:49.817
Come on.

25:03.372 --> 25:09.245
l just don 't know what to do
with myself

25:09.245 --> 25:13.716
Don't know just what to do
with myself

25:13.716 --> 25:17.887
I'm so used to doing

25:17.887 --> 25:20.256
Everything for you

25:20.256 --> 25:25.928
- You suck!
- Planning everything for two

25:25.928 --> 25:29.932
And now that we're through

25:29.932 --> 25:31.734
l just don't know

25:31.734 --> 25:36.539
What to do with my time

25:36.539 --> 25:39.108
I'm so lonesome for you

25:39.108 --> 25:41.243
It's a crime

25:41.243 --> 25:44.906
Going to a movie

26:13.976 --> 26:17.647
lf your new love

26:17.647 --> 26:20.316
Ever turns you down

26:20.316 --> 26:22.451
Come back

26:22.451 --> 26:27.650
I will be around
just waiting for you

26:29.492 --> 26:33.588
l just don 't know what to do

26:34.830 --> 26:37.924
Like a summer rose

26:39.835 --> 26:43.271
